{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1149,"text":"I have spent my entire life"},{"time":4872,"text":"either at the schoolhouse,\non the way to the schoolhouse,"},{"time":9197,"text":"or talking about what happens\nin the schoolhouse."}]},{"cues":[{"time":11820,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":12943,"text":"Both my parents were educators,"},{"time":15255,"text":"my maternal grandparents were educators,"},{"time":18505,"text":"and for the past 40 years,\nI've done the same thing."},{"time":22346,"text":"And so, needless to say, over those years"},{"time":24712,"text":"I've had a chance\nto look at education reform"},{"time":28228,"text":"from a lot of perspectives."},{"time":30059,"text":"Some of those reforms have been good."},{"time":32012,"text":"Some of them have been not so good."},{"time":34282,"text":"And we know why kids drop out."},{"time":36479,"text":"We know why kids don't learn."},{"time":37958,"text":"It's either poverty, low attendance,"},{"time":40875,"text":"negative peer influences..."},{"time":43251,"text":"We know why."},{"time":44888,"text":"But one of the things\nthat we never discuss"},{"time":47235,"text":"or we rarely discuss"},{"time":49547,"text":"is the value and importance\nof human connection."},{"time":53839,"text":"Relationships."}]},{"cues":[{"time":56076,"text":"James Comer says\nthat no significant learning"},{"time":59674,"text":"can occur without\na significant relationship."},{"time":62873,"text":"George Washington Carver says all learning"},{"time":65247,"text":"is understanding relationships."},{"time":69354,"text":"Everyone in this room has been affected\nby a teacher or an adult."},{"time":74946,"text":"For years, I have watched people teach."},{"time":79516,"text":"I have looked at the best\nand I've looked at some of the worst."}]},{"cues":[{"time":82898,"text":"A colleague said to me one time,"},{"time":84720,"text":"\"They don't pay me to like the kids."},{"time":87243,"text":"They pay me to teach a lesson."},{"time":88832,"text":"The kids should learn it."},{"time":90085,"text":"I should teach it, they should learn it,"},{"time":92015,"text":"Case closed.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":93929,"text":"Well, I said to her,"},{"time":96203,"text":"\"You know, kids don't learn\nfrom people they don't like.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":99307,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":101626,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":107220,"text":"She said, \"That's just a bunch of hooey.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":110625,"text":"And I said to her,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":111672,"text":"\"Well, your year is going to be\nlong and arduous, dear.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":116086,"text":"Needless to say, it was."},{"time":117577,"text":"Some people think that you can either\nhave it in you to build a relationship,"},{"time":121363,"text":"or you don't."},{"time":123084,"text":"I think Stephen Covey had the right idea."},{"time":125174,"text":"He said you ought to just\nthrow in a few simple things,"},{"time":128716,"text":"like seeking first to understand,"},{"time":131021,"text":"as opposed to being understood."},{"time":133479,"text":"Simple things, like apologizing."},{"time":136366,"text":"You ever thought about that?"},{"time":137724,"text":"Tell a kid you're sorry, they're in shock."}]},{"cues":[{"time":139904,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":141092,"text":"I taught a lesson once on ratios."},{"time":143521,"text":"I'm not real good with math,\nbut I was working on it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":146546,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":147712,"text":"And I got back and looked\nat that teacher edition."},{"time":150518,"text":"I'd taught the whole lesson wrong."}]},{"cues":[{"time":152346,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":153674,"text":"So I came back to class\nthe next day and I said,"},{"time":155992,"text":"\"Look, guys, I need to apologize."},{"time":158224,"text":"I taught the whole lesson wrong.\nI'm so sorry.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":162070,"text":"They said, \"That's okay, Ms. Pierson."},{"time":163923,"text":"You were so excited, we just let you go.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":170950,"text":"I have had classes that were so low,"},{"time":175418,"text":"so academically deficient, that I cried."},{"time":178831,"text":"I wondered, \"How am I\ngoing to take this group,"},{"time":181807,"text":"in nine months,"},{"time":183878,"text":"from where they are\nto where they need to be?"},{"time":186529,"text":"And it was difficult, it was awfully hard."},{"time":190202,"text":"How do I raise the self-esteem of a child"},{"time":192703,"text":"and his academic achievement\nat the same time?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":195726,"text":"One year I came up with a bright idea."},{"time":197792,"text":"I told all my students,"},{"time":199637,"text":"\"You were chosen to be in my class"},{"time":203278,"text":"because I am the best teacher"},{"time":204826,"text":"and you are the best students,"},{"time":206372,"text":"they put us all together"},{"time":207817,"text":"so we could show\neverybody else how to do it.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":211382,"text":"One of the students said, \"Really?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":213291,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":215575,"text":"I said, \"Really. We have\nto show the other classes"},{"time":218598,"text":"how to do it, so when\nwe walk down the hall,"},{"time":221058,"text":"people will notice us,\nso you can't make noise."},{"time":223609,"text":"You just have to strut.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":225243,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":226460,"text":"And I gave them a saying to say:"},{"time":228136,"text":"\"I am somebody."},{"time":229428,"text":"I was somebody when I came."},{"time":230793,"text":"I'll be a better somebody when I leave."},{"time":232717,"text":"I am powerful, and I am strong."},{"time":234710,"text":"I deserve the education that I get here."},{"time":237400,"text":"I have things to do, people to impress,"},{"time":239792,"text":"and places to go.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":241564,"text":"And they said, \"Yeah!\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":242808,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":244336,"text":"You say it long enough,"},{"time":245756,"text":"it starts to be a part of you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":249189,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":256010,"text":"I gave a quiz, 20 questions."},{"time":259786,"text":"A student missed 18."},{"time":262625,"text":"I put a \"+2\" on his paper\nand a big smiley face."}]},{"cues":[{"time":265951,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":267528,"text":"He said, \"Ms. Pierson, is this an F?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":271276,"text":"I said, \"Yes.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":272632,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":273902,"text":"He said, \"Then why'd you\nput a smiley face?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":277081,"text":"I said, \"Because you're on a roll."},{"time":279329,"text":"You got two right.\nYou didn't miss them all.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":282214,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":283401,"text":"I said, \"And when we review this,\nwon't you do better?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":286820,"text":"He said, \"Yes, ma'am, I can do better.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":289349,"text":"You see, \"-18\" sucks\nall the life out of you."},{"time":292981,"text":"\"+2\" said, \"I ain't all bad.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":300999,"text":"For years, I watched my mother\ntake the time at recess to review,"},{"time":307062,"text":"go on home visits in the afternoon,"},{"time":309894,"text":"buy combs and brushes\nand peanut butter and crackers"},{"time":312653,"text":"to put in her desk drawer\nfor kids that needed to eat,"},{"time":315387,"text":"and a washcloth and some soap\nfor the kids who didn't smell so good."},{"time":318650,"text":"See, it's hard to teach kids who stink."}]},{"cues":[{"time":320936,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":322323,"text":"And kids can be cruel."},{"time":324827,"text":"And so she kept those things in her desk,"},{"time":327403,"text":"and years later, after she retired,"},{"time":330928,"text":"I watched some of those\nsame kids come through"},{"time":333545,"text":"and say to her, \"You know, Ms. Walker,"},{"time":335529,"text":"you made a difference in my life."},{"time":338044,"text":"You made it work for me."},{"time":339280,"text":"You made me feel like I was somebody,"},{"time":341318,"text":"when I knew, at the bottom, I wasn't."},{"time":344705,"text":"And I want you to just\nsee what I've become.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":346832,"text":"And when my mama died two years ago at 92,"},{"time":349955,"text":"there were so many former\nstudents at her funeral,"},{"time":353159,"text":"it brought tears to my eyes,\nnot because she was gone,"},{"time":355873,"text":"but because she left\na legacy of relationships"},{"time":359280,"text":"that could never disappear."}]},{"cues":[{"time":361788,"text":"Can we stand to have more relationships?"},{"time":365535,"text":"Absolutely."},{"time":366714,"text":"Will you like all your children?\nOf course not."}]},{"cues":[{"time":369848,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":371126,"text":"And you know your toughest\nkids are never absent."}]},{"cues":[{"time":375048,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":377041,"text":"Never."},{"time":378681,"text":"You won't like them all,"},{"time":380139,"text":"and the tough ones show up for a reason."},{"time":383549,"text":"It's the connection.\nIt's the relationships."},{"time":392230,"text":"So teachers become\ngreat actors and great actresses,"},{"time":396021,"text":"and we come to work\nwhen we don't feel like it,"},{"time":398284,"text":"and we're listening to policy\nthat doesn't make sense,"},{"time":401334,"text":"and we teach anyway."},{"time":404515,"text":"We teach anyway,\nbecause that's what we do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":408579,"text":"Teaching and learning should bring joy."},{"time":411818,"text":"How powerful would our world be"},{"time":414279,"text":"if we had kids who were\nnot afraid to take risks,"},{"time":418029,"text":"who were not afraid to think,"},{"time":419434,"text":"and who had a champion?"},{"time":420790,"text":"Every child deserves a champion,"},{"time":423255,"text":"an adult who will never give up on them,"},{"time":425465,"text":"who understands the power of connection,"},{"time":428457,"text":"and insists that they become\nthe best that they can possibly be."}]},{"cues":[{"time":432370,"text":"Is this job tough? You betcha."},{"time":434618,"text":"Oh God, you betcha."},{"time":436861,"text":"But it is not impossible."},{"time":440095,"text":"We can do this. We're educators."},{"time":441852,"text":"We're born to make a difference."}]},{"cues":[{"time":444136,"text":"Thank you so much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":445527,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}